The APC National Chairman Comrade Adams Oshiomhole says he made numerous attempts to bring peace in the Edo State chapter of the party. Oshiomhole, who spoke in a television interview, described as “bull sh_t” the allegation that he was playing a godfather’s role in Edo State. APC chieftain insists Oshiomhole playing godfather in Edo Oyegun asks Oshiomhole to stop 'fuelling crisis' in APC, Edo Oyegun asks Oshiomhole to stop fuelling crisis in Edo